  "claim": {
    "id": "CLM-46",
    "text": "On 19 January 2026 soudní exekutor Mgr. Jakub Effenberger (Exekutorský úřad Kolín; case 219 EX 00241/26) issued execution orders against Tomáš Melichárek personally for a debt of 9,327.14 CZK owed to Dopravní podnik hl. m. Prahy, a.s. The orders covered bank accounts, income, movable assets, real estate and his business shares — including his podíl in Able.cz s.r.o. (filed to its Sbírka listin as C 85425/SL69). The execution ended on 24 March 2026 'vymožením' (satisfied by payment) per the termination notice (C 85425/SL70).",
    "status": "VERIFIED_PRIMARY",
    "note": "Exact passages cited in the evidence layer (order pp. 1–4; notice p. 1). The debtor's birth-ID number was redacted per data-minimization practice.",
